description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by Dr. Carolyn Delucia & Cindy Barshop to talk about everything – from vulvas to sexual health to keeping everything ready for when it’s time to get busy.

They discuss how to get your pelvic floor in tip top shape, no matter what stage of life you’re in, why trying to regain trust is harder than you think, but still possible, how to dry things up when you’re TOO wet, and the REAL reasons you may be losing your sex drive – and what you can do to get it back.

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep the show FREE: Woo More Play, GAINSWave, Magic Wand, SiriusXM, Apex

Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily
